MOST IMPORTANT things you’ll want to edit with clear comments so you can tweak your game easily.

🔥 1. PLAYER SETTINGS (speed, fire rate, lives)
var playerSpd = 3;   // ⭐ PLAYER MOVE SPEED (higher = faster ship)
var fireRate  = 15;  // ⭐ SHOOT SPEED (lower = shoots faster)
🔫 2. BULLET SPEED (VERY IMPORTANT)
bullets[pb].y -= 7; // ⭐ PLAYER BULLET SPEED (higher = faster up)
enemyBullets[ab].y += 4; // ⭐ ENEMY BULLET SPEED (higher = faster down)
🚀 3. SHIP TYPES (DIFFERENT STATS)
function startGame(type) {
  shipType  = type;

  playerSpd = type === "viper" ? 3.5 : 2.0; // ⭐ movement speed
  fireRate  = type === "viper" ? 12  : 24;  // ⭐ fire rate
  lives     = type === "viper" ? 2   : 5;   // ⭐ health

👉 Change these to balance ships

👾 4. ALIEN SPEED
var aspd  = (0.5 + wave * 0.2) * boost; // ⭐ ALIEN SPEED

👉 Increase 0.5 to make aliens faster overall

📈 5. DIFFICULTY (WAVES GET HARDER)
var interval = Math.max(30, 90 - wave * 10); // ⭐ HOW FAST ENEMIES SHOOT
Lower = enemies shoot more often
Higher = easier
